{"tid":886880,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"代理行單日新增5項銀主盤　逸峰598萬放售","createTime":"2018-11-02T12:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T13:34:17.000Z","uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f001d07d89d3cd7b20314288cd1cf10011f462","tid":886880,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"世紀21網頁顯示，該行周五新增5個銀主放盤，當中3個為住宅單位。其中粉嶺逸峰5座低層G室，實用面積459方呎，兩房間隔，以598萬元放售，呎價13,028元。世紀21奇豐陳桂新稱，同類單位7月成交價達680萬至700萬元，是次開價較高位低12%至15%。 <br />\n<br />\n其他銀主物業包括位於銅鑼灣的香港大廈低層戶，以及同區廣安大廈中層戶，分別開價1,000萬及900萬元，呎價16,420及13,158元。"},{"pid":"ee6f4e1e3422534ff1acc39453400f715de81e62","tid":886880,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"銀主盤放唔出係咪會拍賣？<br />\n<br />\n放幾耐先拍賣？"},{"pid":"ebbdef10fb5b8ac3cfed4956cfb57f7b1f0a1762","tid":886880,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"唔計！"},{"pid":"9041ff41c5099fa61c9fc38ff5a373b5ee94fcc7","tid":886880,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"銀主都賣13000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10e613a50eeb20816c852acd53f1b955c782a24","tid":886880,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d5c73b951a5b635ca3c48a57329bf059dfdb8da","tid":886880,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9041ff41c5099fa61c9fc38ff5a373b5ee94fcc7","tid":886880,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"銀主都賣13000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"賣唔出收回一件事，銀主開價唔可以平過估價太多"},{"pid":"f38e10bd74aa6feb19c6189247aed789d7d88789","tid":886880,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀主都賣13000<img src=\"/